{"tid":1906702,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[FAILED STATE回力鏢]美國爆搶購潮廁紙勁搶手　網民：首次見Costco無水賣","createTime":"2020-03-02T06:05:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-02T13:08:26.000Z","uid":51469,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"04e3af7540f5a02d1c690d185cefda4b69c248a6","tid":1906702,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T06:05:12.000Z","msg":"美國當局指，該名華盛頓州死者生前沒有證據顯示曾到過高危地方，也未曾與感染者有緊密接觸，認為可能是社區感染。另外，加州及俄勒岡州等都有多宗未能確定感染來源的病例，當局擔心疫情或正在西岸蔓延。<br />\n<br />\n雖然美國總統特朗普呼籲民眾勿陷入恐慌，但多個城市仍有大批市民到Costco搶購糧食和家居用品。各地民眾在twitter上傳照片，顯示加州三藩市及洛衫磯、華盛頓州西雅圖、紐約布魯克林（Brooklyn）、俄勒岡州波特蘭（Portland）和麻省沃爾塞姆（Waltham）等地的Costco，市民購物車上全是飲用水、乾糧食品和廁紙。<br />\n<br />\n有市民目擊搶購情況後驚訝表示，「我第一次看到Costco沒有水賣」、「就算是黑色星期五（Black Friday）、聖誕節或除夕也沒有這麼誇張」、「看來民眾真的被新冠病毒嚇怕了」。網民稱，賣場以廁紙、水、米、罐頭和肉類最為熱銷，店員都忙於上貨，貨架幾乎只剩下氣泡水；至於Costco門外，排隊入場的人龍更遠至停車場。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4082048/org/7a90b5eb95f51836eabd131037d6161b.JPG/1X_c-eR9lEYD7ppiUxAHXT2XHO2M3KVEunZ49rp2ePY\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4082048%2Forg%2F7a90b5eb95f51836eabd131037d6161b.JPG%2F1X_c-eR9lEYD7ppiUxAHXT2XHO2M3KVEunZ49rp2ePY&h=fb31d5bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4082049/org/0176f8ee72c19a27c6d58b4914b0b699.JPG/gQMuLRfOfFMcCTjQZkriw3bIu_j608J9BDEbDQQxGw0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4082049%2Forg%2F0176f8ee72c19a27c6d58b4914b0b699.JPG%2FgQMuLRfOfFMcCTjQZkriw3bIu_j608J9BDEbDQQxGw0&h=e81d1c20&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4082050/org/cd6729a2c6b1bd54f5036af228a2dc4b.JPG/9Am2qgyAzWMTNi5ipvogv9lGKHKSNrvnGz0b1xs9G9c\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4082050%2Forg%2Fcd6729a2c6b1bd54f5036af228a2dc4b.JPG%2F9Am2qgyAzWMTNi5ipvogv9lGKHKSNrvnGz0b1xs9G9c&h=30ea5cc8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.co